		{# ── Office for Ethical Compliance ────────────────────────────────────────── #}
		<div class="post-contents mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

			<section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="heading-ethical-compliance">
				<div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b13634]/30 to-transparent"></span>
					<h2 id="heading-ethical-compliance" class="text-md md:text-lg font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[#b13634]">{{ 'Office for Ethical Compliance'|t }}</h2>
					<span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#b13634]/30 to-transparent"></span>
				</div>

				<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 shadow-sm bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
					<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
						{{ 'All faculty, staff, and students have a responsibility to be aware of all policies that cover items related to ethics. The university is a safe environment for individuals to report suspected unethical behaviour. If you are subject to an unethical behaviour, you should report it to your immediate supervisor (Dean of your school for students) and the Director of Human Resources if that supervisor is not a party to the concern which you raised. If the supervisor is a party to the suspect behaviour, the behaviour should be reported to the Senior Administration Manager of Human Resources and Administration'|t }}
						(<a href="mailto:yusri@cud.ac.ae" class="font-medium text-[#b13634] hover:underline">yusri@cud.ac.ae</a>).
						{{ 'The Human Resources Department must ensure that all employees and students are aware that this kind of disclosure is guaranteed by the university to be possible without fear of reprisal.'|t }}
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<section class="mb-12" aria-labelledby="heading-suggestion-box">
				<div class="mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
					<span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#b13634]/30 to-transparent"></span>
					<h2 id="heading-suggestion-box" class="text-md md:text-lg font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-[#b13634]">{{ 'How to Raise a Concern: Our Suggestion Box'|t }}</h2>
					<span class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-[#b13634]/30 to-transparent"></span>
				</div>

				<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-xl ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 shadow-sm bg-white p-6 sm:p-8">
					<p class="mb-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
						{{ 'To ensure that every member of our community feels safe and supported, we provide multiple avenues for communication, including a physical'|t }}
						<strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">{{ 'Suggestion Box'|t }}</strong>
						{{ 'located on both campuses.'|t }}
					</p>

					<p class="mb-4 text-sm font-medium text-slate-700">{{ 'This service is designed to:'|t }}</p>

					<ul class="mb-0 space-y-4" role="list">
						<li class="flex gap-3">
							<span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#b13634]/10">
								<span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#b13634]"></span>
							</span>
							<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
								<strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">{{ 'Promote Anonymity:'|t }}</strong>
								{{ 'The Suggestion Boxes offer a completely anonymous way to share feedback, report "grave concerns," or act as a whistleblower without the pressure of a face-to-face meeting.'|t }}
							</p>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-3">
							<span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#b13634]/10">
								<span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#b13634]"></span>
							</span>
							<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
								<strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">{{ 'Support Inclusivity:'|t }}</strong>
								{{ 'We recognize that some individuals may feel shy or hesitant to come forward through digital or formal channels; these boxes provide a low-barrier, accessible alternative for everyone.'|t }}
							</p>
						</li>
						<li class="flex gap-3">
							<span class="mt-0.5 flex h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#b13634]/10">
								<span class="h-1.5 w-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#b13634]"></span>
							</span>
							<p class="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
								<strong class="font-semibold text-slate-800">{{ 'Ensure Confidentiality:'|t }}</strong>
								{{ 'All submissions are treated with the utmost seriousness and are reviewed by authorized personnel to ensure that every voice is heard and every concern is addressed with integrity.'|t }}
							</p>
						</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				{# ── Suggestion Box Gallery ── #}
				<div class="mt-8" aria-label="{{ 'Suggestion Box Gallery'|t }}">
					<div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 sm:gap-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">

						<figure class="group overflow-hidden rounded-xl ring-1 ring-slate-900/5 shadow-sm bg-white">
							<div class="overflow-hidden">
